          <p>
           Bumpers College students are advised by a faculty or staff member within their specific
                              major. Students who have already declared a major should check
           <a href="https://uaconnect.uark.edu/">
            UAConnect
           </a>
           for their assigned advisor and contact them directly. Undecided students, or those
                              needing an advisor assigned, please contact the Bumpers College Dean’s Office (AFLS
                              E202) or call
           <a href="tel:+14795752252">
            479-575-2252
           </a>
           .
          </p>
