           Email the school’s academic counselor, Sheri Lynn Tuck, at
           <a href="mailto:stuck@uark.edu">
            stuck@uark.edu
           </a>
           , or schedule an appointment with her through
           <a href="/_resources/downloads/uasuccess-getting-started.pdf">
            UASuccess
           </a>
           . She will go over the program you wish to join.
           <br/>
           <br/>
           To make an appointment in UASuccess, log onto
           <a href="https://learn.uark.edu/">
            Blackboard
           </a>
           , select "UASuccess" in the top right corner, and then select "My Success Network".
                              If you are not currently listed as a Fay Jones student: Select "Services" on the top
                              menu bar, search "Fay Jones", and select the appropriate advisor from the list. The
                              list may take a moment to appear.
