           College of Education and Health Professions has a blended decentralized model of academic
                              advising. Students are assigned professional or faculty advisors in their specific
                              academic department.
          </p>
          <p>
           Students can begin making connections with their academic department by visiting the
                              College's Academic Affairs office (GRAD 317) or calling
           <a href="tel:+1-479-575-4203">
            479-575-4203
           </a>
           .
          </p>
          <p>
           Students who have already declared a major should check
           <a href="https://uaconnect.uark.edu">
            UAConnect
           </a>
